query.sql: Select FullDate, MonthYearNum, Year, DATEPART(wk, ca.FullDate)*10000+Year(ca.FullDate) as WeekYear, UPPER(MonthYear) as MonthYear from utils.calendar as ca
Select FullDate, MonthYearNum, Year, DATEPART(wk, ca.FullDate)*10000+Year(ca.FullDate) as WeekYear, UPPER(MonthYear) as MonthYear from utils.calendar as ca
Select FullDate, MonthYearNum, Year, DATEPART(wk, ca.FullDate)*10000+Year(ca.FullDate) as WeekYear, UPPER(MonthYear) as MonthYear from utils.calendar as ca

select hc.*, UPPER(TO_CHAR(hc.Added, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, CAST(TO_CHAR(hc.Added, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, DATEPART(wk, hc.Added)*10000+Year(hc.Added) as WeekYear, TO_DATE(hc.Added, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, Year(hc.Added) as "Year" from History.ChampionshipPositions hc group by hc.ID
select cc.*, CAST(TO_CHAR(cc.Created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, TO_DATE(cc.Created, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, Year(cc.Created) as "Year", 1 as "Count" from Community.Comment cc

Select 1100000000 + cc.ID as ID, cc.author as Author, cp.Lang as Lang, cc.created as ContributionDate, CAST(TO_CHAR( cc.created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, UPPER(TO_CHAR( cc.created, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, TO_DATE(cc.created, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, DATEPART(wk, cc.created)*10000+Year(cc.created) as WeekYear, Year( cc.created ) as "Year"
from Community.Comment as cc
left join (select cp.ID, cp.Lang from Community.Post as cp) cp on cc.Post = cp.ID
WHERE cc.Post in (select cp.ID from Community.Post as cp WHERE cp.deleted = 0 and cp.published = 1 and cp.PostType != 'Digest') and cc.Deleted = 0 group by cc.ID Union Select 100000000 + cp.Id as ID, cp.author as Author, cp.lang as Lang, cp.created as ContributionDate, CAST(TO_CHAR( cp.created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, UPPER(TO_CHAR( cp.created, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, TO_DATE(cp.created, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, DATEPART(wk, cp.created)*10000+Year(cp.created) as WeekYear, Year( cp.created ) as "Year"
from Community.Post as cp
WHERE deleted = 0 and published = 1 and PostType != 'Digest'

Select DISTINCT Author, Lang, Min(ContributionDate) as ContributionDate, YEAR(Min(ContributionDate)) as Year, Upper(TO_CHAR( TO_TIMESTAMP(CAST(Min(ContributionDate) AS VARCHAR(4000)), 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, CAST(CONVERT(char(6), Min(ContributionDate), 112) AS int) as MonthYearNum, TO_DATE(CAST(Min(ContributionDate) AS VARCHAR(4000)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, DATEPART(wk, Min(ContributionDate))*10000+Year(Min(ContributionDate)) as WeekYear From (Select 1100000000 + cc.ID as ID, cc.author as Author, cp.Lang as Lang, cc.created as ContributionDate
from Community.Comment as cc
left join (Select cp.ID, cp.Lang from Community.Post as cp) cp on cc.Post = cp.ID
WHERE cc.Post in (select cp.ID from Community.Post as cp WHERE cp.deleted = 0 and cp.published = 1 and cp.PostType != 'Digest') and cc.Deleted = 0
Union Select 100000000 + cp.Id as ID, cp.author as Author, cp.lang as Lang, cp.created as ContributionDate
from Community.Post as cp
WHERE deleted = 0 and published = 1 and PostType != 'Digest') Group by Author, Lang

Select 1100000000 + cc.ID as ID, cc.author as Author, cp.Lang as Lang, cc.created as ContributionDate, CAST(TO_CHAR( cc.created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, UPPER(TO_CHAR( cc.created, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, TO_DATE(cc.created, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, DATEPART(wk, cc.created)*10000+Year(cc.created) as WeekYear, Year( cc.created ) as "Year"
from Community.Comment as cc
left join (select cp.ID, cp.Lang from Community.Post as cp) cp on cc.Post = cp.ID
WHERE cc.Post in (select cp.ID from Community.Post as cp WHERE cp.deleted = 0 and cp.published = 1 and cp.PostType != 'Digest') and cc.Deleted = 0
Union Select 100000000 + cp.Id as ID, cp.author as Author, cp.lang as Lang, cp.created as ContributionDate, CAST(TO_CHAR( cp.created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, UPPER(TO_CHAR( cp.created, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, TO_DATE(cp.created, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, DATEPART(wk, cp.created)*10000+Year(cp.created) as WeekYear, Year( cp.created ) as "Year" from Community.Post as cp
WHERE deleted = 0 and published = 1 and PostType != 'Digest' group by cp.ID

select cm.*, CAST(TO_CHAR( cm.Created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, UPPER(TO_CHAR( cm.Created, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, TO_DATE(cm.Created, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, DATEPART(wk, cm.Created)*10000+Year(cm.Created) as WeekYear, Year( cm.Created ) as "Year" from Community.Member cm

select cm.*, CAST(TO_CHAR( cm.Created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, UPPER(TO_CHAR( cm.Created, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, TO_DATE(cm.Created, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, DATEPART(wk, cm.Created)*10000+Year(cm.Created) as WeekYear, Year( cm.Created ) as "Year" from Community.Member cm

select cp.*, UPPER(TO_CHAR(cp.Created, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, CAST(TO_CHAR(cp.Created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, Year(cp.Created) as YearPosts, TO_DATE(CAST(cp.Created AS VARCHAR(4000)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, DATEPART(wk, cp.Created)*10000+Year(cp.Created) as WeekYear, CASE WHEN cp.PostType = 'Article' then 1 else 0 END as CountArticle, case when cp.PostType = 'Question' then 1 else 0 END as CountQuestions, case when cp.PostType = 'Announcement' then 1 else 0 END as CountAnnouncement, case when cp.PostType = 'Discussion' then 1 else 0 END as CountDiscussion, case when Instr(cp.Tags,'Cach',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountTagCache, case when Instr(cp.Tags,'InterSystems IRIS,',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountTagIRIS, case when Instr(cp.Tags,'HealthShare',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountTagHealthShare, case when Instr(cp.Tags,'Ensemble',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountTagEnsemble, case when cp.CommentsAmount = 0 then 'Unanswered' WHEN cp.CommentsAmount != 0 AND cp.HasCorrectAnswer = 0 then 'Answered' else 'Accepted' END as CommentsAmountType FROM Community.Post as cp LEFT JOIN Community.Member cm on cm.Uid = cp.Author WHERE cp.deleted = 0 and cp.published = 1 and cp.PostType != 'Digest'

select hv.*, CAST(TO_CHAR(hv.DateOfData, 'YYYYMM') as Int) as MonthYearNum, UPPER(TO_CHAR(hv.DateOfData, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, DATEPART(wk, hv.DateOfData)*10000+Year(hv.DateOfData) as WeekYear, Year(hv.DateOfData) as "Year", CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'Ensemble', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as EnsembleTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'Cach', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as CacheTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'Atelier', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as AtelierTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'HealthShare', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as HealthShareTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'iKnow', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as iKnowTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'InterSystems IRIS,', 1) > 0 or cp.Tags = 'InterSystems IRIS' then hv.Delta else 0 END as InterSystemsIRISTag, cp.PostType from History.Views hv LEFT JOIN Community.Post as cp on hv.Post = cp.ID WHERE cp.deleted = 0 and cp.published = 1 and cp.PostType != 'Digest'

select hv.*, CAST(TO_CHAR(hv.DateOfData, 'YYYYMM') as Int) as MonthYearNum, UPPER(TO_CHAR(hv.DateOfData, 'MON-YYYY')) as MonthYear, DATEPART(wk, hv.DateOfData)*10000+Year(hv.DateOfData) as WeekYear, Year(hv.DateOfData) as "Year", CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'Ensemble', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as EnsembleTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'Cach', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as CacheTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'Atelier', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as AtelierTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'HealthShare', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as HealthShareTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'iKnow', 1) > 0 then hv.Delta else 0 END as iKnowTag, CASE WHEN Instr(cp.Tags, 'InterSystems IRIS,', 1) > 0 or cp.Tags = 'InterSystems IRIS' then hv.Delta else 0 END as InterSystemsIRISTag, cp.PostType from History.Views hv LEFT JOIN Community.Post as cp on hv.Post = cp.ID WHERE cp.deleted = 0 and cp.published = 1 and cp.PostType != 'Digest'
